Subscribe 
To subscribe to one of our podcasts, use a podcasting app on your computer, smartphone or tablet. 
For iPhone, iPad and iPod touch, use the Podcasts app (this may come pre-installed on your device). Search for the name of the show you'd like to subscribe to and choose the subscribe option. 
For Android devices, try Pocket Casts or Stitcher . Use the subscribe or favorite options in these apps to automatically get new episodes. 
For more information on all of our podcasts, visit http://www.sctimes.com/podcast . 
Latest episode: Episode 006 - Border Battle Special 
Tech and Apollo renew their football rivalry at St. Cloud State and Sartell travels to Sauk Rapids for the Storm's homecoming game. Plus, a look at other key area football matchups.
